'''Moox Live''' was a [[Norway|Norwegian]] television channel in 2006–2007 with [[user-generated content]]. The viewers could vote for music videos, watch interviews with celebrities and discuss topics such as [[movie]]s, [[fashion]], celebrities, [[sex]] and love. It was taken off the air after less than one year.
