'''Seronga Airport''' {{airport codes | |FB71 |}} is an airport serving the village of [[Seronga]] in the [[North-West District (Botswana)|North-West District]] of [[Botswana]]. The well-marked runway is on the northern edge of the [[Okavango Delta]].
